Package: container
Type: Package
Title: Example package that uses the container-based infrastructure from Travis
Version: 1.0
Date: 2015-07-28
Author: Jan Tilly
Maintainer: Jan Tilly <jtilly@econ.upenn.edu>
Description: Example R package that is built using the container-based
    infrastructure from Travis. See here for more details:
    http://docs.travis-ci.com/user/workers/container-based-infrastructure/
    This package depends on ggplot2, Rcpp, RcppArmadillo to showcase that it
    can be build quickly despite all the clutter.
License: GPL-2
Imports: Rcpp (>= 0.11.6)
Depends: ggplot2
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
Suggests: testthat
VignetteBuilder: knitr
